s** tab.\n\n**To clear the highlighted selection**\n\n-   Right-click the selection, and then click **Clear Selection**.\n\n## Related topics\n\n\n[WPA Common Scenarios](windows-performance-analyzer-common-scenarios.md)\n\n \n\n \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n"}